comments: Zubac (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in LaVine's (CHI) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Vucevic (CHI) makes marginal contact with George's (LAC) hand after the release of his jump shot attempt.
LaVine (CHI) makes marginal contact with Zubac's (LAC) side and disengages as they pursue the loose ball.
Vucevic (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Batum's (LAC) path and does not deliver contact.
Batum (LAC) jumps towards DeRozan (CHI) and makes marginal contact to his hand after the release his jump shot attempt.
Caruso (CHI) places his forearm to George's (LAC) front at the start of his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Batum (LAC) places his arm to DeRozan's (CHI) side as he defends over the pick and maintains legal guarding position as he loses control of the ball on his own.
DeRozan (CHI) initiates contact to George's (LAC) lower body and the contact affects his SQBR.
Covington (LAC) extends a hand into DeRozan's (CHI) back and affects his SQBR during the driving shot attempt.
Jackson (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Caruso's (CHI) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
LaVine (CHI) places his arm to George's (LAC) front defending his drive to the basket and marginal contact occurs.
Caruso (CHI) and Covington (LAC) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
LaVine (CHI) briefly engages with Jackson (LAC) off ball and disengages.
George (LAC) moves slightly into Caruso's (CHI) space and he is able to defend through the marginal contact.
Green (CHI) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Covington (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position defending DeRozan's (CHI) drive to the basket.
Covington (LAC) cleanly dislodges the pass attempt to Green (CHI) before incidental contact occurs.
Jackson (LAC) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with LaVine's (CHI) arm that does not affect his shot attempt.
DeRozan (CHI) commits a take foul on George (LAC).
Mann (LAC) briefly engages with DeRozan (CHI) and disengages as he gathers the inbound pass.
Vucevic (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Batum's (LAC) path with his arm slightly extended and makes margianl contact as they separate.
Mann (LAC) briefly places his hand to DeRozan's (CHI) side at the start of his drive and disengages.
LaVine (CHI) briefly places his hand to George's (LAC) side and slides his hand off as he gathers the inbound pass.
Caruso (CHI) commits a take foul on Covington (LAC).
White (CHI) is already in Covington's (LAC) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Mann (LAC) places an arm around DeRozan's (CHI) opposite-side hip and the contact affects his FOM during the throw-in.
George (LAC) makes incidental foot to foot contact with LaVine (CHI) as he sets the pick and disengages.
George (LAC) jumps from point A to point B and initiates contact to DeRozan's (CHI) lower body that affects his jump shot attempt.  DeRozan does not overtly extend his leg to create the contact.
Hartenstein (LAC) and Williams (CHI) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Vucevic (CHI) intentionally kicks the ball.
Zubac (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Caruso's (CHI) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Vucevic (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Batum's (LAC) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Caruso (CHI) places two slightly extended arms against Batum's (LAC) body as he sets the pick and releases away from the contact.
Batum (LAC) moves forward into DeRozan (CHI) and marginal contact occurs as he makes the pass.
Kennard (LAC) makes marginal contact with Williams (CHI) that he is able to move through to finish at the rim with his dunk attempt unaffected.
Zubac (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Caruso's (CHI) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Zubac (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in LaVine's (CHI) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Batum (LAC) briefly engages with DeRozan's (CHI) body prior to the inbound pass and disengages.
Batum (LAC) briefly grasps Vucevic's (CHI) jersey during the screen and the contact does not affect his FOM.
Vucevic (CHI) already in Batum's (LAC) path with his arm slightly extended and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Zubac (LAC) establishes himself firming up in Caruso's (CHI) path and makes marginal contact to his lower body as they disengage.
Williams (CHI) makes contact with Jackson's (LAC) arm after his gather, and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Kennard (LAC) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Batum (LAC) makes contact with DeRozan's (CHI) arm after his gather, and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Jackson (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Williams' (CHI) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Zubac (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in LaVine's (CHI) path and absorbs the contact.
Jackson (LAC) places his off-arm against Caruso (CHI) and disengages as he comes to a pause.
LaVine (CHI) briefly grasps Zubac's (LAC) jersey in the lane and immediately disengages.
Zubac (LAC) is deemed to be in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Zubac (LAC) makes marginal contact to LaVine's (CHI) shoulder underneath the basket and disengages as they pursue the loose ball.

LaVine (CHI) legally contest Jackson's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
